headline: Christmas Spirit Delivered One Truckload at a Time
summary: FT. CAMPBELL, Ky., December 18, 2024--‘Tis the season for giving, and FedEx is helping the Christmas SPIRIT Foundation deliver holiday happiness to military families across the U.S. This year marks a milestone year of the Trees for Troops program. Over the last two decades, more than 300,000 Christmas trees have been delivered to troops and their families.
